
1️⃣ Uninstall MySQL
bash
Copy
Edit
brew services stop mysql
brew uninstall mysql
Remove leftover data/config:

bash
Copy
Edit
rm -rf /opt/homebrew/var/mysql
rm -rf /opt/homebrew/etc/my.cnf*
2️⃣ Uninstall MongoDB
bash
Copy
Edit
brew services stop mongodb-community@7.0
brew uninstall mongodb-community@7.0
brew untap mongodb/brew
Remove leftover data/config:

bash
Copy
Edit
rm -rf /opt/homebrew/var/mongodb
rm -rf /opt/homebrew/etc/mongod.conf
3️⃣ Check if completely removed
bash
Copy
Edit
brew list
brew services list
If they don’t appear there, they’re gone.

